thread.title_full: First Aid Kits Australia reviewed by Peter

author: Peter
title: Peter
text:
Ordered a medical kit for my business. Exactly what I ordered and delivered promptly. Initially thought we had been forgotten only to find out that we had received it and a staff member packed it away.Rachel Williams was very helpful in tracking the delivery.
Great service and product.
Peter
Panarottis
Macarthur
